Playwright Homepage
Homepage should have correct page Title
Homepage should have a Footer section
Homepage should have Navigation Menu
Homepage should have a Header section
Playwright Menu
Menu (Large screen) should have link for 'Docs'
Menu (Large screen) should have link for 'Node.js'
Menu (Large screen) should have link for 'API'
Menu (Large screen) should have homepage link to 'Playwright'
Menu (Large screen) should have drop down menu for other languages
Menu (Large screen) should change menu links when Java language is selected
Menu (Large screen) should have link for 'Community'
Menu (Large screen) should change menu links when python language is selected
Menu (Large screen) should change menu links when .NET language is selected
Menu (Small screen) should have link for 'Docs'
Menu (Small screen) should have homepage link to 'Playwright'
Menu (Small screen) should have link for 'API'
Menu (Small screen) should have link for 'Node.js'
Menu (Small screen) should change menu links when python language is selected
Menu (Small screen) should have drop down menu for other languages
Menu (Small screen) should have link for 'Community'
Menu (Small screen) should change menu links when Java language is selected
Menu (Small screen) should change menu links when .NET language is selected
Add Todo
Item can be added to ToDo list
The input field should be cleared when the item is added
Item should be appended to the bottom of the list
Clear Completed Todo
The 'Clear Completed' button is hidden when there are no completed items
The 'Clear Completed' button is visible when there are completed items
The 'Clear Completed' button should remove completed items
Complete Todo
Completed item can be marked as active again
All items can be marked as completed in one click
All items checkbox should be initially unchecked
Items can be marked as complete
All completed items can be marked as incomplete in one click
Todo Counter
The counter should increase when an item is added
The counter should decrease WHEN an item is completed
The counter should display 0 items left WHEN all items are complete
The counter should decrease WHEN an item is deleted
Delete Todo
The delete button should be visible when hovering over an item
An item can be removed from using the delete button
An item can be removed when an empty text string is entered during edit
Edit Todo
Complete Checkbox should be hidden when editing
Edits are saved when the edit field is unfocused
Edits are saved when Enter is pressed
Whitespace before and after text is removed when saving
Cancel edit by using escape
Todo Filters
There should be 3 filters available when there are items on the list
The 'All' filter should show active and completed items
The 'Active' filter should show only active items
The 'Completed' filter should only show completed items
